The '''Financial Reform Act''' was a bill introduced to the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] in [[23 BBY/Legends|23 BBY]]. The goal of the bill was to address and reduce the amount of corruption that was causing the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] to stagnate. However, after the [[Assassin/Legends|assassination]] of [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Jheramahd Greyshade]], and the revelation that he had been [[Death/Legends|murdered]] by [[Tsian]] on [[Venco Autem]]'s orders in an attempt to prevent the bill's passage, the Act never got to a vote.

Shortly afterwards, the first systems began to secede from the Republic, and the failure of the Financial Reform Act to pass was viewed by many as the cause of the exacerbation of the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]], which ultimately led to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

